title: (Fri Full) Jimmie Allen on Taking Time Off to be a Pro Bowler, His New album and How Kane Brown Confused Bobby for Him + Bobby’s No. 1 90’s Country Music Video
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Jimmie Allen on Taking Time Off to be a Pro Bowler, His New album and How Kane Brown Confused Bobby for Him + Bobby’s No. 1 90’s Country Music Video
description:
Jimmie Allen stops by to talk about his new album, Tulip Drive. He reveals why he wants to take time off from music to become a pro bowler. Bobby shares how he embarrassed himself after a text exchange with Kane Brown. Bobby has been listing his Top 5 90’s country music videos all week…today we arrive at No. 1!
